                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">线性结构完整，翻译上佳</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="840193859">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-840193859" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-840193859" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="840193859">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/PoliticalPotato/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-06-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">从纯粹审美来说，最喜爱18世纪马刀配洋枪的时代。工业魔法和武士技艺并进，骑兵铁蹄和排枪齐射争锋。制式化思维尚未吞食工匠奇思，火器的使用却给武器制造赋予新的思路。于是“风琴炮”、“神火飞鸦”这种浪漫派武器最终呈现在我们眼前。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="477484635">
